---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="💀 Manifesto — CyperX.dev" activeNav="manifesto">

  <!-- Chaos sticker (tablet+) -->
  <div class="chaos-sticker sticker-red hidden sm:block" style="position: absolute; top: 1rem; right: 1rem; z-index: 40; transform: rotate(4deg);">ROOT_ACCESS</div>

  <div class="fractal-card w-full max-w-5xl relative overflow-visible transition-colors duration-300 reveal-element active">
    <!-- Skull Watermark -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-[0.03] pointer-events-none select-none z-0">
      <span class="text-[10rem] sm:text-[20rem]">💀</span>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-ascii-border hidden sm:block">
      &lt;sk&gt;💀&lt;/sk&gt; ............................................................. &lt;sk&gt;💀&lt;/sk&gt;
    </div>

    <div class="absolute inset-0 glitch-bg pointer-events-none mix-blend-screen opacity-60 z-10"></div>
    <span class="absolute -bottom-4 sm:-bottom-8 -right-2 sm:-right-8 text-3xl sm:text-6xl mix-blend-exclusion z-30 hover:scale-110 hover:-rotate-12 transition-transform cursor-pointer drop-shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(255,0,255,0.8)]">💀🦞🤙😎</span>
    <span class="absolute -top-3 sm:-top-6 -left-2 sm:-left-6 text-2xl sm:text-5xl mix-blend-difference z-30 opacity-90 drop-shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,249,249,0.8)]">👾🦞🤙</span>

    <div class="terminal-header bg-[#FF003C] px-3 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-3 flex items-center border-b-[3px] border-primary relative z-20 transition-colors duration-300">
      <h2 class="text-base sm:text-chaos-xl glitch-intense text-white font-bold leading-tight tracking-widest uppercase truncate">root@shredder:~</h2>
      <div class="ml-auto flex gap-2 sm:gap-3 flex-shrink-0">
        <div class="size-3 sm:size-4 rounded-sm bg-[#050505] border border-primary"></div>
        <div class="size-3 sm:size-4 rounded-sm bg-[#050505] border border-primary"></div>
        <div class="size-3 sm:size-4 rounded-sm bg-primary border border-primary"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="terminal-body p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-10 space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 relative z-20 min-h-[400px] sm:min-h-[500px] transition-colors duration-300">
      <!-- whoami -->
      <div class="reveal-element">
        <div class="text-primary text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-2 flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 sm:mr-3 text-[#FF003C] animate-pulse">#</span>
          <span class="typewriter inline-block dark:text-white text-black text-base sm:text-xl">whoami</span>
        </div>
        <div class="text-primary/80 font-mono text-xs sm:text-sm ml-4 sm:ml-6 italic">
          DIGITAL_CORRUPTOR // GLITCH_MAXIMALIST // VOID_WALKER
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="glitch-bar-static"></div>

      <!-- cat manifesto -->
      <div class="pt-2 reveal-element">
        <div class="text-primary text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4 flex items-center">
          <span class="mr-2 sm:mr-3">&gt;</span>
          <span class="typewriter inline-block dark:text-white text-black text-sm sm:text-base">cat manifesto.txt</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6 text-base sm:text-xl text-slate-100 leading-relaxed border-l-4 sm:border-l-[6px] border-[#FF003C] pl-4 sm:pl-6 ml-1 sm:ml-2 bg-[#111111]/80 p-3 sm:p-4 transition-colors duration-300">
          <p class="glitch-text opacity-95 text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-xl">
            I am the ghost in the machine learning model. A digital psychonaut carving paths through latent spaces and concrete waves.
            My blood is <span class="text-primary font-black uppercase tracking-wider">50% monster energy</span> and <span class="text-[#FF00FF] font-black uppercase tracking-wider">50% unresolved segfaults</span>.
          </p>
          <p class="text-slate-300 dark:text-slate-300 transition-colors text-sm sm:text-base">
            I build AI tools that hallucinate brutalist realities. When I'm not untangling prompt injections, I'm breaking bones on halfpipes.
            The physical world is just a slow, legacy API. <span class="dark:text-white text-black font-bold bg-[#FF003C]/20 px-1">We are compiling a new counter-culture.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- ASCII Block -->
      <div class="ascii-block chaos-rotate-n1 text-[10px] sm:text-sm overflow-hidden">
        ▓▓▓ MANIFESTO_LOADED :: REALITY_OVERWRITE_PENDING ▓▓▓
        ░░░ COUNTER_CULTURE.EXE → RUNNING :: EXIT_CODE: NEVER ░░░
      </div>

      <div class="glitch-bar-static"></div>

      <!-- ls skills -->
      <div class="pt-4 sm:pt-6 reveal-element">
        <div class="text-primary text-lg sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-4 sm:mb-6 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-2">
          <span class="mr-2 sm:mr-3">&gt;</span>
          <span class="typewriter inline-block dark:text-white text-black text-xs sm:text-base">ls -la /sys/modules/skills/</span>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-2 sm:space-y-3 font-mono text-sm sm:text-lg ml-2 sm:ml-4">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-[#111111]/50 p-2 border border-primary/20 hover:border-primary transition-colors flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 sm:px-3 py-1 border border-primary font-bold shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,249,249,0.3)] text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">[OK]</span>
            <span class="text-slate-200 text-xs sm:text-sm">Claude_Code_Integration.so</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-auto text-xs hidden md:block">0x00A1</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-[#111111]/50 p-2 border border-primary/20 hover:border-primary transition-colors flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 sm:px-3 py-1 border border-primary font-bold shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,249,249,0.3)] text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">[OK]</span>
            <span class="text-slate-200 text-xs sm:text-sm">Kickflips_v2.dll</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-auto text-xs hidden md:block">0x00B2</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-[#FF003C]/10 p-2 border border-[#FF003C]/30 relative overflow-hidden flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-[#FF003C] bg-[#FF003C]/20 px-2 sm:px-3 py-1 border border-[#FF003C] font-bold glitch-text relative z-10 text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">[FAIL]</span>
            <span class="text-slate-400 line-through opacity-80 relative z-10 text-xs sm:text-sm">Corporate_Compliance.exe</span>
            <span class="text-[#FF003C] ml-auto text-xs font-bold animate-pulse relative z-10 hidden sm:block">ERR_CORE_DUMP</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 sm:gap-4 bg-[#111111]/50 p-2 border border-primary/20 hover:border-[#FF00FF] transition-colors flex-wrap">
            <span class="text-primary bg-primary/10 px-2 sm:px-3 py-1 border border-primary font-bold shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(6,249,249,0.3)] text-xs sm:text-sm flex-shrink-0">[OK]</span>
            <span class="text-[#FF00FF] font-bold text-xs sm:text-sm" style="text-shadow: 1px 0 #06f9f9, -1px 0 #FF003C;">Psilocybin_Protocol.sys</span>
            <span class="text-slate-500 ml-auto text-xs hidden md:block">0x00D4</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Active Prompt -->
      <div class="text-primary text-2xl sm:text-3xl mt-8 sm:mt-12 flex items-center font-bold reveal-element">
        <span class="mr-3 sm:mr-4">&gt;</span>
        <span class="w-3 h-6 sm:w-4 sm:h-8 bg-primary animate-blink-caret shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(6,249,249,0.8)]"></span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Corrupt block -->
  <div class="corrupt-block w-full max-w-5xl"></div>

  <!-- Fragment_A Section -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl reveal-element chaos-rotate-1">
    <div class="fractal-card p-4 sm:p-8 relative overflow-hidden torn-top">
      <div class="absolute -left-6 sm:-left-10 -bottom-6 sm:-bottom-10 opacity-[0.05] pointer-events-none select-none">
        <span class="text-[8rem] sm:text-[15rem]">💀</span>
      </div>
      <div class="chaos-sticker sticker-magenta hidden sm:block" style="position: absolute; top: -1rem; right: -1rem; z-index: 20;">Fragment_A :: Neural_Lattice</div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 items-center relative z-10">
        <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-chaos-xl glitch-intense tracking-tighter uppercase">Building the Void</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm sm:text-base">Our architectures don't just host data; they breathe interference. We design for the collapse, for the beauty of the broken signal. 🦞🤙</p>
          <div class="h-1 w-24 bg-primary"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-video bg-[#050505] border-2 border-[#FF00FF]/40 relative overflow-hidden group">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1550684848-fac1c5b4e853?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80')] bg-cover opacity-50 grayscale hover:grayscale-0 transition-all duration-700"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 glitch-bg mix-blend-overlay"></div>
          <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity">
            <span class="text-white font-bold bg-[#FF00FF] px-3 py-1 sm:px-4 sm:py-2 uppercase text-xs">Access Link</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Chaos divider -->
  <div class="chaos-divider w-full max-w-5xl"></div>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-5xl reveal-element mb-8 sm:mb-24 collage-pull-up">
    <div class="fractal-card p-4 sm:p-8 relative overflow-hidden chaos-rotate-n1">
      <div class="chaos-sticker sticker-acid hidden sm:block" style="position: absolute; bottom: -1rem; right: 2rem; z-index: 20;">HALFPIPE_SINGULARITY</div>
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 relative z-10">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-5xl sm:text-7xl text-[#FF003C] animate-pulse">leak_add</span>
        <h3 class="text-xl sm:text-chaos-2xl glitch-intense uppercase tracking-widest break-words">The Singularity is a Halfpipe</h3>
        <p class="max-w-xl text-sm sm:text-lg text-slate-400 italic">"The error is the only honest part of the system. In the glitch, we find the truth that the clean code tries to hide." 🦞</p>
        <div class="flex gap-3 sm:gap-4 flex-wrap justify-center">
          <button class="px-5 sm:px-8 py-2 sm:py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-bold hover:bg-primary hover:text-black transition-all uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer text-sm sm:text-base">Connect</button>
          <button class="px-5 sm:px-8 py-2 sm:py-3 bg-[#FF003C] text-white font-bold hover:brightness-125 transition-all uppercase tracking-widest cursor-pointer text-sm sm:text-base">Disconnect</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
